data.meta_description: Attachment Report - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides acknowledgements for a work related learning report on ZISCO Marketing department. It thanks various people and departments that supported the learning, including family, university supervisors, the ZISCO training department, and several managers and employees in the Export Sales and Customer Services departments that provided assistance. ZISCO is acknowledged as offering the work placement opportunity during the learning period.
